<html lang="FR-fr">
<head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8'>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge"/>
    <title>Lajavel</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Lajavel is a new Java Web Framework made for hardcore developers."/>
    <meta name="keywords" content="lajavel,laravel,framework"/>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ assets(css) }}">
    <script src="{{ assets(js) }}" async></script>
    {% include tailwind %}
</head>

<body>
<!-- Navigation -->
{% include header %}

<!-- Hero -->
<section
        class="pt-24 md:mt-0 md:h-screen flex flex-col justify-center text-center md:text-left md:flex-row md:justify-between md:items-center lg:px-48 md:px-12 px-4 bg-secondary">
    <div class="md:flex-1 md:mr-10">
        <h1 class="font-pt-serif text-5xl font-bold mb-7">
            Lajavel, made for a
            <span class="bg-underline1 bg-left-bottom bg-no-repeat pb-2 bg-100%">
          cleaner code
        </span>
        </h1>
        <p class="font-pt-serif font-normal mb-7">
            Lajavel has been made in a way for your code to be clean all the time.
            It's the best framework on the market, rated five stars by Mr. Clean and sponsored
            by My Digital School.
        </p>
        <img src='{{ mds.imageUrl }}' alt="MDS" class="w-56"/>
    </div>
    <div class="flex justify-around md:block mt-10 md:mt-0 md:flex-1">
        <div class="relative">
            <img src='images/Highlight1.svg' alt="" class="absolute -top-6"/>
        </div>
        <img src='images/mrclean.png' alt="Mr Clean"/>
        <div class="relative">
            <img src='images/Highlight2.svg' alt="" class="absolute -bottom-10 -right-6"/>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- How it works -->
<section class="bg-black text-white sectionSize">
    <div>
        <h2 class="secondaryTitle bg-underline2 bg-100%">How it works</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row">
        <div class="flex-1 mx-8 flex flex-col items-center my-4">
            <div class="border-2 rounded-full bg-secondary text-black h-12 w-12 flex justify-center items-center mb-3">
                1
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-montserrat font-medium text-xl mb-2">Download</h3>
            <p class="text-center font-montserrat">
                Using NPM or the Github Release.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1 mx-8 flex flex-col items-center my-4">
            <div class="border-2 rounded-full bg-secondary text-black h-12 w-12 flex justify-center items-center mb-3">
                2
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-montserrat font-medium text-xl mb-2">Install</h3>
            <p class="text-center font-montserrat">
                You just have to follow the tutorial.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1 mx-8 flex flex-col items-center my-4">
            <div class="border-2 rounded-full bg-secondary text-black h-12 w-12 flex justify-center items-center mb-3">
                3
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-montserrat font-medium text-xl mb-2">Code</h3>
            <p class="text-center font-montserrat">
                Make the world shine through your usage of Lajavel.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Features -->
<section class="sectionSize bg-secondary">
    <div>
        <h2 class="secondaryTitle bg-underline3 bg-100%">Features</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="md:grid md:grid-cols-2 md:grid-rows-2">

        <div class="flex items-start font-montserrat my-6 mr-10">
            <img src='images/logos/Heart.svg' alt='' class="h-7 mr-4"/>
            <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-2xl">Fast</h3>
                <p>
                    Lajavel is optimized in order to run faster than all our concurrent.
                    With the cleanest code on the market, we are sure that you will be
                    satisfied with the speed of our framework.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start font-montserrat my-6 mr-10">
            <img src='images/logos/Heart.svg' alt='' class="h-7 mr-4"/>
            <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-2xl">Dynamic</h3>
                <p>
                    You can implement all your assets dynamically in Lajavel.
                    It could be CSS, JS, JAVEL, it all works with just one mention in the code.
                    This is the future of coding.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start font-montserrat my-6 mr-10">
            <img src='images/logos/Heart.svg' alt='' class="h-7 mr-4"/>
            <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-2xl">MVC</h3>
                <p>
                    Lajavel follows the MVC Design Pattern, and is the first one to apply
                    in such a perfect way. This is what you can except from our
                    fresh framework.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start font-montserrat my-6 mr-10">
            <img src='images/logos/Heart.svg' alt='' class="h-7 mr-4"/>
            <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-2xl">Errors</h3>
                <p>
                    When you get errors in your code, it always gets a bit messy.
                    But Lajavel comes in clutch with a clean way to display errors.
                    You will never get lost in your code again.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>

<!-- Pricing -->
<section class="sectionSize bg-secondary py-0">
    <div>
        <h2 class="secondaryTitle bg-underline4 mb-0 bg-100%">Pricing</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="flex w-full flex-col md:flex-row">

        <div class='flex-1 flex flex-col mx-6 shadow-2xl relative bg-secondary rounded-2xl py-5 px-8 my-8 md:top-24'>
            <h3 class="font-pt-serif font-normal text-2xl mb-4">
                Extrait de Javel
            </h3>
            <div class="font-montserrat font-bold text-2xl mb-4">
                $2
                <span class="font-normal text-base"> / month</span>
            </div>

            <div class="flex">
                <img src='images/logos/CheckedBox.svg' alt="" class="mr-1"/>
                <p>Keeps the floor clean</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex">
                <img src='images/logos/CheckedBox.svg' alt="" class="mr-1"/>
                <p>Runs faster</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex">
                <img src='images/logos/CheckedBox.svg' alt="" class="mr-1"/>
                <p>Mr. Clean kisses you</p>
            </div>

            <button class=" border-2 border-solid border-black rounded-xl text-lg py-3 mt-4">
                Choose plan
            </button>
        </div>

        <div class='flex-1 flex flex-col mx-6 shadow-2xl relative bg-secondary rounded-2xl py-5 px-8 my-8 md:top-12'>
            <h3 class="font-pt-serif font-normal text-2xl mb-4">
                Eau de Javel
            </h3>
            <div class="font-montserrat font-bold text-2xl mb-4">
                $5
                <span class="font-normal text-base"> / month</span>
            </div>

            <div class="flex">
                <img src='images/logos/CheckedBox.svg' alt="" class="mr-1"/>
                <p>Cleanest water on earth</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex">
                <img src='images/logos/CheckedBox.svg' alt="" class="mr-1"/>
                <p>Mr. Clean sleeps with you</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex">
                <img src='images/logos/CheckedBox.svg' alt="" class="mr-1"/>
                <p>Lajavel accepts your PR</p>
            </div>

            <button class=" border-2 border-solid border-black rounded-xl text-lg py-3 mt-4">
                Choose plan
            </button>
        </div>

        <div class='flex-1 flex flex-col mx-6 shadow-2xl relative bg-secondary rounded-2xl py-5 px-8 my-8 md:top-24'>
            <h3 class="font-pt-serif font-normal text-2xl mb-4">
                Eau de Labarraque
            </h3>
            <div class="font-montserrat font-bold text-2xl mb-4">
                $10
                <span class="font-normal text-base"> / month</span>
            </div>

            <div class="flex">
                <img src='images/logos/CheckedBox.svg' alt="" class="mr-1"/>
                <p>Mr. Clean is all yours</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex">
                <img src='images/logos/CheckedBox.svg' alt="" class="mr-1"/>
                <p>You can work for Lajavel</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex">
                <img src='images/logos/CheckedBox.svg' alt="" class="mr-1"/>
                <p>You get a free mop</p>
            </div>

            <button class=" border-2 border-solid border-black rounded-xl text-lg py-3 mt-4">
                Choose plan
            </button>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>

<!-- FAQ  -->
<section class="sectionSize items-start pt-8 md:pt-36 bg-black text-white">
    <div>
        <h2 class="secondaryTitle bg-highlight3 p-10 mb-0 bg-center bg-100%">
            FAQ
        </h2>
    </div>

    <div toggleElement class="w-full py-4">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
            <div question class="font-montserrat font-medium mr-auto">
                What is Lajavel?
            </div>
            <img src='images/logos/CaretRight.svg' alt="" class="transform transition-transform"/>
        </div>
        <div answer class="font-montserrat text-sm font-extralight pb-8 hidden">
            Lajavel is a Java Web Framework made with the purpose of writing cleaner code.
        </div>
    </div>
    <hr class="w-full bg-white"/>

    <div toggleElement class="w-full py-4">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
            <div question class="font-montserrat font-medium mr-auto">
                Is is free?
            </div>
            <img src='images/logos/CaretRight.svg' alt="" class="transform transition-transform"/>
        </div>
        <div answer class="font-montserrat text-sm font-extralight pb-8 hidden">
            Yes! Being clean is always free. But you can get even shinier with our premium plans.
        </div>
    </div>
    <hr class="w-full bg-white"/>

    <div toggleElement class="w-full py-4">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
            <div question class="font-montserrat font-medium mr-auto">
                Am I awesome?
            </div>
            <img src='images/logos/CaretRight.svg' alt="" class="transform transition-transform"/>
        </div>
        <div answer class="font-montserrat text-sm font-extralight pb-8 hidden">
            Yes! No doubt about it.
        </div>
    </div>
    <hr class="w-full bg-white"/>

</section>

<!-- Footer -->
{% include footer %}
</body>

</html>